第四课 三脚架和稳定器使用示范

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appmv4tTYbQ7433/v_5b14f83fde963_7HPy77cc

<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">淘系短视频最终目的</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">是提高销量</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/70409800_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; caret-color: red; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/><br/></p></section><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">毫无疑问，2018年是属于短视频的一年。一方面抖音迅速崛起，在抖音中植入商品信息，成为了淘宝店重要的流量入口；另一方面，自淘宝商品视频化以来 ，淘宝对于短视频的投入越来越重视，商品视频化已成为一个不可逆转的趋势。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/78245600_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbfxqt5cdh9jhvla1x1p4ofwb4cvn40pw4cfjxa2qbl3ib7gt55yytdfa/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">尤其今年更是短视频的风口，随着5g的即将到来，人们对视频的需求越来越大。图文信息不再能满足大部分人的信息获取需求求，因为视频更加地直观。以商品为例，一个小的短视频不仅可以清晰地360度无死角地展现产品，最完美地将产品细节展现在镜头前，更能构建产品的使用价值。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">短视频已经成为了卖家必备的技能。卖家做短视频可以让消费者更加清晰了解自己的产品，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">用视频讲故事，给产品赋予灵魂</strong>，好的产品短视频可以对产品的售卖起到至关重要的作用。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">淘系短视频区别与抖音短视频，淘宝短视频更注重的是内容还有信息，抖音主要是娱乐化，两者的需求点不一样。对于卖家而言，短视频最终目的是提高销量，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">如果宝贝卖不出去，谈短视频就是耍流氓</strong>。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/96489400_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hb4ibkict5meeeohgrwzbk6lybz0q5uht10ur1gubucrljca1zicgdqlgga/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; z-index: -1; cursor: pointer; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">短视频怎么做：</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">三种方式怎么选？</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/6271300_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; caret-color: red; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">主图短视频、详情页短视频、微淘短视频怎么做？外包给专业的拍摄机构还是招聘专门的视频人才、购买专业的拍摄设备？或是自己尝试用手机拍摄？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">无论是哪一种，这三种情况应该包含大多数卖家短视频制作的方式。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">1-外包</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px; caret-color: red;">卖家可以甩掉一些包袱，解决技术问题，但是沟通成本较高，还要一笔不小费用。更关键的是，外包的作品，往往很难让人满意，因为没有人会比你更懂你的产品。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">2-买设备养团队</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：理想的情况下，这可能是最好的方法。拥有自己的团队和设备，就有无限的可能，可以最大化发挥短视频的价值。但是人力与物力的成本，对于中小卖家来说并非最好的选择。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">3-手机拍</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍最大的好处是可以省去一大笔人力和专业设备费用，简单好上手。但是大多数卖家随手用手机拍出来的作品，格调难登大雅之堂，更不能突出宝贝卖点，对于宝贝来说不仅不能成为提高销量的加分项，甚至会影响顾客对宝贝的第一印象。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">三种方式各有千秋又各有缺陷。那么卖家如何才能降低短视频的拍摄成本，还能拍出高大上高转化的短视频呢？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/13742400_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hb1ro4l6jzrr5rnibtvgxoz3eszcvgilnsmbi6lvoib59vbdh9immipz8g/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">Q</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：如何降低视频拍摄的时间成本和设备成本？</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 133, 155);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">A</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：降低视频拍摄的时间成本就是拍摄之前要做到心中有数，要把前期功课做好，写好拍摄的脚本与分镜头，知道要拍摄的内容和镜头以后时间就会省了很多；手机+辅助工具拍摄相比专业的重设备，可以降低很大一部分成本。只需要花几百块买一个辅助工具就能满足拍摄需求。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">Q</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍摄视频和专业设备相比，是否会降低视频质量？</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 133, 155);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">A</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍摄与专业设备拍摄相比，并不会降低视频质量。因为现在有很多手机拍摄辅助工具，比如手机镜头等。加上如今用户基本都在移动端观看淘系短视频，手机+辅助工具完全能达到短视频拍摄要求。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px;">拿起手机讲述</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px;">自己的产品故事</span></strong></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/21693100_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">对于中小卖家来说，如果用手机便能拍出想要的效果，尝试手机拍摄不失为一种好方法。关键在于，如何脱离小打小闹的手机拍摄方式，让手机也能拍出符合宝贝调性的高转化短视频。让用户了解到淘宝短视频背后的故事，简单的操作简单的工具也可以完成意想不到的效果。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/40466600_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbdkf16ywm5ucmyeeaeqfz1sa0hfkib1y8omymvxzbxek4nonsdffveg/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">美摄年度红人</span>@阿玛尼打造《淘宝短视频速成课》，让你用手机就能完成淘宝短视频的拍摄</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">这门短视频拍摄课程从浅入深，不需要专业的拍摄设备，也不需要专业的拍摄基础，从手机基本操作到实践产品拍摄，帮助中小卖家得到意想不到的收获 ，自己独立就能完成头图视频。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">让我们拿起手机为自己的产品讲述不一样的故事！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">讲师介绍</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/51843700_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/63261500_1527040827.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="阿玛尼-介绍.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">课程目录</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/73530400_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/27673400_1527048967.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="阿玛尼课程目录详情.jpg"/></p></section></section>

第三课  如何低成本的选择手机配套装备

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appmv4tTYbQ7433/v_5b14f83fde910_5HfuFSW3

<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">淘系短视频最终目的</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">是提高销量</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/70409800_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; caret-color: red; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/><br/></p></section><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">毫无疑问，2018年是属于短视频的一年。一方面抖音迅速崛起，在抖音中植入商品信息，成为了淘宝店重要的流量入口；另一方面，自淘宝商品视频化以来 ，淘宝对于短视频的投入越来越重视，商品视频化已成为一个不可逆转的趋势。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/78245600_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbfxqt5cdh9jhvla1x1p4ofwb4cvn40pw4cfjxa2qbl3ib7gt55yytdfa/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">尤其今年更是短视频的风口，随着5g的即将到来，人们对视频的需求越来越大。图文信息不再能满足大部分人的信息获取需求求，因为视频更加地直观。以商品为例，一个小的短视频不仅可以清晰地360度无死角地展现产品，最完美地将产品细节展现在镜头前，更能构建产品的使用价值。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">短视频已经成为了卖家必备的技能。卖家做短视频可以让消费者更加清晰了解自己的产品，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">用视频讲故事，给产品赋予灵魂</strong>，好的产品短视频可以对产品的售卖起到至关重要的作用。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">淘系短视频区别与抖音短视频，淘宝短视频更注重的是内容还有信息，抖音主要是娱乐化，两者的需求点不一样。对于卖家而言，短视频最终目的是提高销量，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">如果宝贝卖不出去，谈短视频就是耍流氓</strong>。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/96489400_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hb4ibkict5meeeohgrwzbk6lybz0q5uht10ur1gubucrljca1zicgdqlgga/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; z-index: -1; cursor: pointer; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">短视频怎么做：</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">三种方式怎么选？</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/6271300_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; caret-color: red; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">主图短视频、详情页短视频、微淘短视频怎么做？外包给专业的拍摄机构还是招聘专门的视频人才、购买专业的拍摄设备？或是自己尝试用手机拍摄？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">无论是哪一种，这三种情况应该包含大多数卖家短视频制作的方式。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">1-外包</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px; caret-color: red;">卖家可以甩掉一些包袱，解决技术问题，但是沟通成本较高，还要一笔不小费用。更关键的是，外包的作品，往往很难让人满意，因为没有人会比你更懂你的产品。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">2-买设备养团队</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：理想的情况下，这可能是最好的方法。拥有自己的团队和设备，就有无限的可能，可以最大化发挥短视频的价值。但是人力与物力的成本，对于中小卖家来说并非最好的选择。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">3-手机拍</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍最大的好处是可以省去一大笔人力和专业设备费用，简单好上手。但是大多数卖家随手用手机拍出来的作品，格调难登大雅之堂，更不能突出宝贝卖点，对于宝贝来说不仅不能成为提高销量的加分项，甚至会影响顾客对宝贝的第一印象。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">三种方式各有千秋又各有缺陷。那么卖家如何才能降低短视频的拍摄成本，还能拍出高大上高转化的短视频呢？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/13742400_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hb1ro4l6jzrr5rnibtvgxoz3eszcvgilnsmbi6lvoib59vbdh9immipz8g/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">Q</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：如何降低视频拍摄的时间成本和设备成本？</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 133, 155);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">A</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：降低视频拍摄的时间成本就是拍摄之前要做到心中有数，要把前期功课做好，写好拍摄的脚本与分镜头，知道要拍摄的内容和镜头以后时间就会省了很多；手机+辅助工具拍摄相比专业的重设备，可以降低很大一部分成本。只需要花几百块买一个辅助工具就能满足拍摄需求。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">Q</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍摄视频和专业设备相比，是否会降低视频质量？</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 133, 155);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">A</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍摄与专业设备拍摄相比，并不会降低视频质量。因为现在有很多手机拍摄辅助工具，比如手机镜头等。加上如今用户基本都在移动端观看淘系短视频，手机+辅助工具完全能达到短视频拍摄要求。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px;">拿起手机讲述</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px;">自己的产品故事</span></strong></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/21693100_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">对于中小卖家来说，如果用手机便能拍出想要的效果，尝试手机拍摄不失为一种好方法。关键在于，如何脱离小打小闹的手机拍摄方式，让手机也能拍出符合宝贝调性的高转化短视频。让用户了解到淘宝短视频背后的故事，简单的操作简单的工具也可以完成意想不到的效果。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/40466600_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbdkf16ywm5ucmyeeaeqfz1sa0hfkib1y8omymvxzbxek4nonsdffveg/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">美摄年度红人</span>@阿玛尼打造《淘宝短视频速成课》，让你用手机就能完成淘宝短视频的拍摄</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">这门短视频拍摄课程从浅入深，不需要专业的拍摄设备，也不需要专业的拍摄基础，从手机基本操作到实践产品拍摄，帮助中小卖家得到意想不到的收获 ，自己独立就能完成头图视频。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">让我们拿起手机为自己的产品讲述不一样的故事！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">讲师介绍</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/51843700_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/63261500_1527040827.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="阿玛尼-介绍.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">课程目录</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/73530400_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/27673400_1527048967.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="阿玛尼课程目录详情.jpg"/></p></section></section>

第二课  苹果手机短视频基础秘籍

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appmv4tTYbQ7433/v_5b14f83fde8af_Tnon0DOp

<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">淘系短视频最终目的</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">是提高销量</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/70409800_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; caret-color: red; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/><br/></p></section><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">毫无疑问，2018年是属于短视频的一年。一方面抖音迅速崛起，在抖音中植入商品信息，成为了淘宝店重要的流量入口；另一方面，自淘宝商品视频化以来 ，淘宝对于短视频的投入越来越重视，商品视频化已成为一个不可逆转的趋势。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/78245600_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbfxqt5cdh9jhvla1x1p4ofwb4cvn40pw4cfjxa2qbl3ib7gt55yytdfa/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">尤其今年更是短视频的风口，随着5g的即将到来，人们对视频的需求越来越大。图文信息不再能满足大部分人的信息获取需求求，因为视频更加地直观。以商品为例，一个小的短视频不仅可以清晰地360度无死角地展现产品，最完美地将产品细节展现在镜头前，更能构建产品的使用价值。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">短视频已经成为了卖家必备的技能。卖家做短视频可以让消费者更加清晰了解自己的产品，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">用视频讲故事，给产品赋予灵魂</strong>，好的产品短视频可以对产品的售卖起到至关重要的作用。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">淘系短视频区别与抖音短视频，淘宝短视频更注重的是内容还有信息，抖音主要是娱乐化，两者的需求点不一样。对于卖家而言，短视频最终目的是提高销量，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">如果宝贝卖不出去，谈短视频就是耍流氓</strong>。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/96489400_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hb4ibkict5meeeohgrwzbk6lybz0q5uht10ur1gubucrljca1zicgdqlgga/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; z-index: -1; cursor: pointer; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">短视频怎么做：</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">三种方式怎么选？</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/6271300_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; caret-color: red; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">主图短视频、详情页短视频、微淘短视频怎么做？外包给专业的拍摄机构还是招聘专门的视频人才、购买专业的拍摄设备？或是自己尝试用手机拍摄？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">无论是哪一种，这三种情况应该包含大多数卖家短视频制作的方式。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">1-外包</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px; caret-color: red;">卖家可以甩掉一些包袱，解决技术问题，但是沟通成本较高，还要一笔不小费用。更关键的是，外包的作品，往往很难让人满意，因为没有人会比你更懂你的产品。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">2-买设备养团队</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：理想的情况下，这可能是最好的方法。拥有自己的团队和设备，就有无限的可能，可以最大化发挥短视频的价值。但是人力与物力的成本，对于中小卖家来说并非最好的选择。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">3-手机拍</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍最大的好处是可以省去一大笔人力和专业设备费用，简单好上手。但是大多数卖家随手用手机拍出来的作品，格调难登大雅之堂，更不能突出宝贝卖点，对于宝贝来说不仅不能成为提高销量的加分项，甚至会影响顾客对宝贝的第一印象。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">三种方式各有千秋又各有缺陷。那么卖家如何才能降低短视频的拍摄成本，还能拍出高大上高转化的短视频呢？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/13742400_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hb1ro4l6jzrr5rnibtvgxoz3eszcvgilnsmbi6lvoib59vbdh9immipz8g/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">Q</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：如何降低视频拍摄的时间成本和设备成本？</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 133, 155);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">A</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：降低视频拍摄的时间成本就是拍摄之前要做到心中有数，要把前期功课做好，写好拍摄的脚本与分镜头，知道要拍摄的内容和镜头以后时间就会省了很多；手机+辅助工具拍摄相比专业的重设备，可以降低很大一部分成本。只需要花几百块买一个辅助工具就能满足拍摄需求。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">Q</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍摄视频和专业设备相比，是否会降低视频质量？</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 133, 155);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">A</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍摄与专业设备拍摄相比，并不会降低视频质量。因为现在有很多手机拍摄辅助工具，比如手机镜头等。加上如今用户基本都在移动端观看淘系短视频，手机+辅助工具完全能达到短视频拍摄要求。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px;">拿起手机讲述</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px;">自己的产品故事</span></strong></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/21693100_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">对于中小卖家来说，如果用手机便能拍出想要的效果，尝试手机拍摄不失为一种好方法。关键在于，如何脱离小打小闹的手机拍摄方式，让手机也能拍出符合宝贝调性的高转化短视频。让用户了解到淘宝短视频背后的故事，简单的操作简单的工具也可以完成意想不到的效果。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/40466600_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbdkf16ywm5ucmyeeaeqfz1sa0hfkib1y8omymvxzbxek4nonsdffveg/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">美摄年度红人</span>@阿玛尼打造《淘宝短视频速成课》，让你用手机就能完成淘宝短视频的拍摄</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">这门短视频拍摄课程从浅入深，不需要专业的拍摄设备，也不需要专业的拍摄基础，从手机基本操作到实践产品拍摄，帮助中小卖家得到意想不到的收获 ，自己独立就能完成头图视频。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">让我们拿起手机为自己的产品讲述不一样的故事！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">讲师介绍</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/51843700_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/63261500_1527040827.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="阿玛尼-介绍.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">课程目录</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/73530400_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/27673400_1527048967.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="阿玛尼课程目录详情.jpg"/></p></section></section>

第一课 华为mate曝光 对焦 锁焦技巧

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appmv4tTYbQ7433/v_5b14f83fde849_zN5khSkQ

<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">淘系短视频最终目的</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">是提高销量</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/70409800_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; caret-color: red; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/><br/></p></section><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">毫无疑问，2018年是属于短视频的一年。一方面抖音迅速崛起，在抖音中植入商品信息，成为了淘宝店重要的流量入口；另一方面，自淘宝商品视频化以来 ，淘宝对于短视频的投入越来越重视，商品视频化已成为一个不可逆转的趋势。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/78245600_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbfxqt5cdh9jhvla1x1p4ofwb4cvn40pw4cfjxa2qbl3ib7gt55yytdfa/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">尤其今年更是短视频的风口，随着5g的即将到来，人们对视频的需求越来越大。图文信息不再能满足大部分人的信息获取需求求，因为视频更加地直观。以商品为例，一个小的短视频不仅可以清晰地360度无死角地展现产品，最完美地将产品细节展现在镜头前，更能构建产品的使用价值。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">短视频已经成为了卖家必备的技能。卖家做短视频可以让消费者更加清晰了解自己的产品，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">用视频讲故事，给产品赋予灵魂</strong>，好的产品短视频可以对产品的售卖起到至关重要的作用。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">淘系短视频区别与抖音短视频，淘宝短视频更注重的是内容还有信息，抖音主要是娱乐化，两者的需求点不一样。对于卖家而言，短视频最终目的是提高销量，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">如果宝贝卖不出去，谈短视频就是耍流氓</strong>。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/96489400_1527040826.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hb4ibkict5meeeohgrwzbk6lybz0q5uht10ur1gubucrljca1zicgdqlgga/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; z-index: -1; cursor: pointer; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">短视频怎么做：</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">三种方式怎么选？</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/6271300_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; letter-spacing: 0.5px; caret-color: red; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">主图短视频、详情页短视频、微淘短视频怎么做？外包给专业的拍摄机构还是招聘专门的视频人才、购买专业的拍摄设备？或是自己尝试用手机拍摄？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">无论是哪一种，这三种情况应该包含大多数卖家短视频制作的方式。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">1-外包</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px; caret-color: red;">卖家可以甩掉一些包袱，解决技术问题，但是沟通成本较高，还要一笔不小费用。更关键的是，外包的作品，往往很难让人满意，因为没有人会比你更懂你的产品。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">2-买设备养团队</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：理想的情况下，这可能是最好的方法。拥有自己的团队和设备，就有无限的可能，可以最大化发挥短视频的价值。但是人力与物力的成本，对于中小卖家来说并非最好的选择。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">3-手机拍</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍最大的好处是可以省去一大笔人力和专业设备费用，简单好上手。但是大多数卖家随手用手机拍出来的作品，格调难登大雅之堂，更不能突出宝贝卖点，对于宝贝来说不仅不能成为提高销量的加分项，甚至会影响顾客对宝贝的第一印象。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">三种方式各有千秋又各有缺陷。那么卖家如何才能降低短视频的拍摄成本，还能拍出高大上高转化的短视频呢？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/13742400_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hb1ro4l6jzrr5rnibtvgxoz3eszcvgilnsmbi6lvoib59vbdh9immipz8g/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">Q</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：如何降低视频拍摄的时间成本和设备成本？</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 133, 155);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">A</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：降低视频拍摄的时间成本就是拍摄之前要做到心中有数，要把前期功课做好，写好拍摄的脚本与分镜头，知道要拍摄的内容和镜头以后时间就会省了很多；手机+辅助工具拍摄相比专业的重设备，可以降低很大一部分成本。只需要花几百块买一个辅助工具就能满足拍摄需求。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">Q</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍摄视频和专业设备相比，是否会降低视频质量？</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(49, 133, 155);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; font-size: 15px;">A</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">：手机拍摄与专业设备拍摄相比，并不会降低视频质量。因为现在有很多手机拍摄辅助工具，比如手机镜头等。加上如今用户基本都在移动端观看淘系短视频，手机+辅助工具完全能达到短视频拍摄要求。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px;">拿起手机讲述</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 19px;">自己的产品故事</span></strong></p><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/21693100_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbsrk6slupzficvoex5nmibvlrpoh6fmdvkr1viafxtl6qrrr97ewol4ia9q/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit; font-size: 17.1429px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">对于中小卖家来说，如果用手机便能拍出想要的效果，尝试手机拍摄不失为一种好方法。关键在于，如何脱离小打小闹的手机拍摄方式，让手机也能拍出符合宝贝调性的高转化短视频。让用户了解到淘宝短视频背后的故事，简单的操作简单的工具也可以完成意想不到的效果。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnJALKqkS7963/image/ueditor/40466600_1527040827.cn/mmbiz_gif/jdyc7tay4wl7b7tolsg01gnxm2iacj1hbdkf16ywm5ucmyeeaeqfz1sa0hfkib1y8omymvxzbxek4nonsdffveg/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">美摄年度红人</span>@阿玛尼打造《淘宝短视频速成课》，让你用手机就能完成淘宝短视频的拍摄</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">这门短视频拍摄课程从浅入深，不需要专业的拍摄设备，也不需要专业的拍摄基础，从手机基本操作到实践产品拍摄，帮助中小卖家得到意想不到的收获 ，自己独立就能完成头图视频。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;">让我们拿起手机为自己的产品讲述不一样的故事！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 2em;"><span style="m